<p>John and Dave end the month of March with this episode discussing the default settings of both Microsoft Word and Pages, and some issues with both, then they move on to some important nuances when choosing a format for your hard drives. Also discussed are streaming audio to multiple sets of speakers, even if they&rsquo;re connected to the same Mac! All this and more enclosed within. Subscribe today, support your two favorite geeks, download, and enjoy!</p>
<p>Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
